.TH "nvme_init_get_log_reachability_groups" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_reachability_groups" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_reachability_groups \- Initialize passthru command for Retrieve Reachability Groups
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_reachability_groups
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "bool rgo "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_reachability_groups_log *log "  ","
.BI "__u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "rgo" 12
Return groups only
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the log page
.IP "len" 12
The allocated length of the log page
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_REACHABILITY_GROUPS
